name: Thirty third birthday
description:
Happy music,accompanied with dance gives me and all people across the world a positive energy.

This video has been made with warm colour of red which is my personal colour and has been used in my works.

In my thirt third birthday this video has enabled me to be able to transfer a good feeling ,to the audience with warm colour and cheering music and dance in these very bitter and cold world.

But the real form of dance becomes gradually minimal and transformed to the shape of some colourfull squares.
